    "In Firebase Console: Project settings → Your apps → Web app → copy the `firebaseConfig` object. Paste it below. Mini-App Preview loads the compat SDK and sets `window.__caocapFirestore` and optional `window.__caocapFirestoreDefaultPath`.": {},
    "Incomplete": {
      "comment": "A label describing a challenge that has not been completed.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true
    },
    "intro.step0.message": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "كل مهمة تبدأ في لحظة هادئة—عندما تقرر أنك مستعد. تلك اللحظة هي الآن."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Every mission begins in a quiet moment—when you decide you are ready. That moment is now."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "intro.step0.title": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "العد التنازلي للإطلاق."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Countdown to launch."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "intro.step1.message": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "الخوف أثقل على الأرض. تخطَّه—السماء ملك لمن يجرؤ على الصعود."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fear is heaviest on the ground. Push through—the sky belongs to anyone willing to rise."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "intro.step1.title": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "اخترق الغلاف الجوي."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Break atmosphere."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "intro.step2.message": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "التعلّم قوس طويل عبر سماء مفتوحة. ثق بكل خطوة—أنت بالفعل في طريقك."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Learning is a long arc across open sky. Trust each step—you are already on your way."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "intro.step2.title": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "حدِّد اتجاهك."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Find your bearing."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "intro.step3.message": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "من المدار، تبدو الحدود القديمة صغيرة. ما بدا مستحيلاً هو فقط أبعد مما سافرت حتى الآن."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "From orbit, old limits look small. What felt impossible is only farther than you have traveled yet."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "intro.step3.title": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "المنظر يغيّر كل شيء."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The view changes everything."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "intro.step4.message": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "القمر ليس حكراً على الأبطال. ينتظر من يجرؤ على المحاولة. مهمتك تبدأ الآن."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The moon is not reserved for heroes. It waits for anyone brave enough to try. Your mission starts now."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "intro.step4.title": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "خطوة صغيرة واحدة."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "One small step."
          }
        }
      }
    },
